{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775870377830,"sessionID":"ses_285e27dfcffeJkaP47XzFuVBZN","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1f7efc0010uyw1m2iSuuRNE","messageID":"msg_d7a1de68e001mMOJViFKKd5MIg","sessionID":"ses_285e27dfcffeJkaP47XzFuVBZN","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-7d35f2cd3f084df895cd7793f3051a2f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md","content":"# AR-021 — CLI build 命令 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-021 — CLI build 命令 |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: DockerService Enhancements (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Add `get_image_info()` method to `DockerService`\n  - Extract image_id, image_size, and format size to human-readable string\n  - Signature: `get_image_info(image_name: str, tag: str) -> Dict[str, Any]`\n  - Return: `{\"image_id\": str, \"image_size\": str}`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py::TestDockerService::test_get_image_info -v`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2**: Add `_format_size()` helper method to `DockerService`\n  - Convert bytes to human-readable format (e.g., \"125.3 MB\")\n  - Handle KB, MB, GB ranges\n  - Private method used by `get_image_info()`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py::TestDockerService::test_format_size -v`\n\n- [ ] **T1.3**: Update `build_image()` method signature and return structure\n  - Add `dockerfile_path` parameter (separate from context_path)\n  - Add `build_args` parameter for proxy support\n  - Return `{\"image_name\": str, \"image_id\": str, \"image_size\": str, \"build_time\": float, \"tag\": str}`\n  - Stream build logs when `verbose=True`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py::TestDockerService::test_build_image_with_proxy -v`\n\n- [ ] **T1.4**: Add `check_docker_available()` method improvements\n  - Return `True/False` boolean (already exists, verify correctness)\n  - Log Docker daemon status in verbose mode\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py::TestDockerService::test_check_docker_available -v`\n\n### Phase 2: BuildRuntime Class (ST-2)\n\n- [ ] **T2.1**: Create `BuildRuntime` class skeleton in `build_runtime.py`\n  - Import dependencies: `Path`, `Dict`, `Any`, `Optional`\n  - Import services: `MetadataService`, `DockerService`\n  - Define constructor: `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n  - Initialize `self.verbose`, `self._metadata_service`, `self._docker_service`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime.build_runtime import BuildRuntime\"`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2**: Implement `build()` main entry method\n  - Signature: `build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`\n  - Load metadata via `self._metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)`\n  - Store `original_version = metadata.version` for rollback\n  - Call `_validate_build_prerequisites(workspace_path)`\n  - Call `_increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)` → returns `new_tag`\n  - Call `_build_local()` or `_build_cloud()` based on `metadata.build_mode`\n  - Call `_update_build_metadata()` on success\n  - Rollback version on failure, raise `RuntimeError`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_build_local_success -v`\n\n- [ ] **T2.3**: Implement `_validate_build_prerequisites()` method\n  - Check `self._docker_service.check_docker_available()` → raise `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available\")`\n  - Check `workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\"` exists → raise `ValueError(\"Dockerfile not found\")`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_build_docker_unavailable -v`\n\n### Phase 3: Version Increment Logic (ST-3)\n\n- [ ] **T3.1**: Implement `_increment_version()` method\n  - Import `semver` library\n  - Handle valid semver `X.Y.Z` → bump_patch → `X.Y.(Z+1)`\n  - Handle `v`-prefixed non-semver `vX.Y` → append `.1` → `vX.Y.1`\n  - Handle non-semver string → append `-1` → `custom-1`\n  - Handle `None/empty` → return `\"latest\"`\n  - Save updated `metadata.version` via `self._metadata_service.save_metadata()`\n  - Return new tag string\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_version_increment_semver -v`\n\n- [ ] **T3.2**: Add version rollback logic in `build()` method\n  - Store `original_version` before increment\n  - On exception in build: `metadata.version = original_version`\n  - Call `self._metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)`\n  - Raise `RuntimeError(f\"Build failed: {e}. Version rolled back to {original_version}\")`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_version_rollback_on_failure -v`\n\n### Phase 4: Build Execution Methods (ST-4)\n\n- [ ] **T4.1**: Implement `_build_local()` method\n  - Resolve image_name: `metadata.agent_name`\n  - Build args: `{\"PROXY\": options.get(\"proxy\")}` if proxy provided\n  - Call `self._docker_service.build_image()` with:\n    - `dockerfile_path=workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\"`\n    - `context_path=workspace_path`\n    - `image_name=metadata.agent_name`\n    - `tag=new_tag`\n    - `build_args=build_args`\n  - Return build result dict\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_build_local_success -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2**: Implement `_build_cloud()` placeholder method\n  - Check `metadata.build_mode == \"cloud\"`\n  - Return placeholder dict: `{\"image_name\": metadata.agent_name, \"image_id\": \"cloud-placeholder\", \"image_size\": \"0 MB\", \"build_time\": 0, \"tag\": \"latest\"}`\n  - Log warning: `\"Cloud build not implemented\"`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_build_cloud_placeholder -v`\n\n- [ ] **T4.3**: Implement `_update_build_metadata()` method\n  - Update `metadata.image` dict with:\n    - `\"image_name\": build_result[\"image_name\"]`\n    - `\"image_id\": build_result[\"image_id\"]`\n    - `\"image_size\": build_result[\"image_size\"]`\n    - `\"build_time\": build_result[\"build_time\"]`\n    - `\"tag\": tag`\n  - Call `self._metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_update_build_metadata -v`\n\n### Phase 5: CLI Command Implementation (ST-5)\n\n- [ ] **T5.1**: Add `build` command to `main.py`\n  - Import `BuildRuntime` from `agentcube.runtime.build_runtime`\n  - Define Typer command with options:\n    - `workspace: str = \".\"` (alias `-f`, `--workspace`)\n    - `proxy: Optional[str] = None` (alias `-p`, `--proxy`)\n    - `cloud_provider: Optional[str] = None` (`--cloud-provider`)\n    - `output: Optional[str] = None` (`--output`)\n    - `verbose: bool = False` (`--verbose`)\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `kubectl-agentcube build --help`\n\n- [ ] **T5.2**: Implement `build` command handler\n  - Resolve workspace path: `Path(workspace).resolve()`\n  - Initialize `BuildRuntime(verbose=verbose)`\n  - Use Rich Progress spinner: `progress.add_task(\"Building agent image...\", total=None)`\n  - Call `runtime.build(workspace_path, proxy=proxy, cloud_provider=cloud_provider, output=output)`\n  - Print success output with Rich formatting:\n    - `[green]Build completed successfully[/green]`\n    - `Image: {image_name}:{tag}`\n    - `Image ID: {image_id}`\n    - `Size: {image_size}`\n    - `Build time: {build_time}s`\n  - Handle errors via `_handle_error(e, \"build\", verbose)`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_pack_cli.py -v` (update test)\n\n### Phase 6: Unit Tests - BuildRuntime (ST-6)\n\n- [ ] **T6.1**: Create test file `test_build_runtime.py`\n  - Import `pytest`, `unittest.mock`, `Path`\n  - Import `BuildRuntime`, `AgentMetadata`\n  - Create fixtures: `mock_docker_service`, `mock_metadata_service`, `tmp_workspace`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **T6.2**: Test `build_local_success`\n  - Mock DockerService to return valid build result\n  - Mock MetadataService to load/save metadata\n  - Verify build returns correct result dict\n  - Verify metadata.version incremented\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_build_local_success -v`\n\n- [ ] **T6.3**: Test `build_docker_unavailable`\n  - Mock `check_docker_available()` to return `False`\n  - Expect `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_build_docker_unavailable -v`\n\n- [ ] **T6.4**: Test `build_missing_dockerfile`\n  - Create tmp workspace without Dockerfile\n  - Expect `ValueError(\"Dockerfile not found in workspace\")`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_build_missing_dockerfile -v`\n\n- [ ] **T6.5**: Test version increment scenarios\n  - Test semver: `1.2.3` → `1.2.4`\n  - Test v-prefix semver: `v1.2.3` → `v1.2.4`\n  - Test v-prefix non-semver: `v1.0` → `v1.0.1`\n  - Test non-semver: `custom` → `custom-1`\n  - Test empty: `None` → `\"latest\"`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_version_increment -v`\n\n- [ ] **T6.6**: Test version rollback on failure\n  - Mock `build_image()` to raise `BuildError`\n  - Verify metadata.version restored to original\n  - Verify `RuntimeError` raised with rollback message\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_version_rollback_on_failure -v`\n\n- [ ] **T6.7**: Test `build_cloud_placeholder`\n  - Set `metadata.build_mode = \"cloud\"`\n  - Verify placeholder dict returned\n  - Verify warning logged\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py::TestBuildRuntime::test_build_cloud_placeholder -v`\n\n### Phase 7: Unit Tests - DockerService (ST-7)\n\n- [ ] **T7.1**: Create/update `test_docker_service.py`\n  - Test `check_docker_available()` with mocked Docker client\n  - Test `build_image()` with mocked `client.images.build()`\n  - Test `get_image_info()` with mocked image object\n  - Test `_format_size()` helper method\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.2**: Test `build_image_with_proxy`\n  - Mock Docker build API\n  - Pass `build_args={\"PROXY\": \"http://proxy.example.com:8080\"}`\n  - Verify buildargs passed to Docker API\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py::TestDockerService::test_build_image_with_proxy -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.3**: Test `get_image_info`\n  - Mock image with `id=\"sha256:abc123\"` and `attrs[\"Size\"]=125300000`\n  - Verify returns `{\"image_id\": \"sha256:abc123\", \"image_size\": \"125.3 MB\"}`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py::TestDockerService::test_get_image_info -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.4**: Test `_format_size` helper\n  - Test bytes: `500` → `\"500 B\"`\n  - Test KB: `1024` → `\"1.0 KB\"`\n  - Test MB: `1048576` → `\"1.0 MB\"`\n  - Test GB: `1073741824` → `\"1.0 GB\"`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py::TestDockerService::test_format_size -v`\n\n### Phase 8: Integration Tests (ST-8)\n\n- [ ] **T8.1**: Create integration test `test_build_integration.py`\n  - Test full workflow: validate → increment → build → update metadata\n  - Use tmp workspace with Dockerfile and agent_metadata.yaml\n  - Mock Docker SDK for build execution\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_integration.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_integration.py -v`\n\n- [ ] **T8.2**: Test `build_after_pack` integration\n  - Pack creates Dockerfile, build succeeds\n  - Verify metadata.image updated correctly\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_integration.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_integration.py::TestBuildIntegration::test_build_after_pack -v`\n\n- [ ] **T8.3**: Test `rebuild_increments_version` integration\n  - First build: `version=\"v1.0\"` → `tag=\"v1.0.1\"`\n  - Second build: `version=\"v1.0.1\"` → `tag=\"v1.0.2\"`\n  - Verify version increments on each build\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_integration.py`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_integration.py::TestBuildIntegration::test_rebuild_increments_version -v`\n\n### Phase 9: Dependencies & Validation (ST-9)\n\n- [ ] **T9.1**: Add `semver` dependency to `pyproject.toml`\n  - Version: `semver>=3.0.0`\n  - Purpose: Semantic version parsing and bumping\n  - File: `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`\n  - Verification: `pip install semver && python -c \"import semver\"`\n\n- [ ] **T9.2**: Update `runtime/__init__.py` exports\n  - Add `BuildRuntime` to exports\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n  - Verification: `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime import BuildRuntime\"`\n\n- [ ] **T9.3**: Run all tests with coverage\n  - `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing`\n  - Coverage target: >80% for `build_runtime.py`\n  - File: `cmd/cli/tests/`\n  - Verification: `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v --cov=agentcube`\n\n- [ ] **T9.4**: Run lint and type check\n  - `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/`\n  - `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/`\n  - Fix any lint/type errors\n  - File: `cmd/cli/agentcube/`\n  - Verification: `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/ && mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/`\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1.1 → T1.2 → T1.3 → T1.4\n           ↓\n        T2.1 → T2.2 → T2.3\n               ↓\n        T3.1 → T3.2\n               ↓\n        T4.1 → T4.2 → T4.3\n               ↓\n        T5.1 → T5.2\n               ↓\n        T6.1 → T6.2 → T6.3 → T6.4 → T6.5 → T6.6 → T6.7\n               ↓\n        T7.1 → T7.2 → T7.3 → T7.4\n               ↓\n        T8.1 → T8.2 → T8.3\n               ↓\n        T9.1 → T9.2 → T9.3 → T9.4\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| DockerService tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py -v` |\n| BuildRuntime tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py -v` |\n| Integration tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/test_build_integration.py -v` |\n| All tests | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v` |\n| Coverage | `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing` |\n| Build command help | `kubectl-agentcube build --help` |\n| Lint check | `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n| Type check | `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n| Import test | `python -c \"from agentcube.runtime.build_runtime import BuildRuntime\"` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] `BuildRuntime` class defined with `__init__`, `build`, `_validate_build_prerequisites`\n- [ ] `_increment_version()` handles semver, v-prefix, non-semver, None cases\n- [ ] `_build_local()` calls DockerService with correct parameters\n- [ ] `_build_cloud()` returns placeholder for cloud mode\n- [ ] `_update_build_metadata()` updates `metadata.image` dict\n- [ ] Version rollback on build failure\n- [ ] `build` Typer command with all options: `--workspace`, `--proxy`, `--cloud-provider`, `--output`, `--verbose`\n- [ ] Rich Progress spinner during build\n- [ ] Success output: image name, ID, size, build time\n- [ ] Error handling via `_handle_error()`\n- [ ] DockerService `get_image_info()` method\n- [ ] DockerService `_format_size()` helper\n- [ ] DockerService `build_image()` with `build_args` support\n- [ ] Unit tests for version increment scenarios\n- [ ] Unit tests for rollback logic\n- [ ] Unit tests for Docker unavailable/missing Dockerfile\n- [ ] Integration tests for build workflow\n- [ ] Integration test for pack→build workflow\n- [ ] Integration test for rebuild version increment\n- [ ] `semver>=3.0.0` dependency added\n- [ ] `BuildRuntime` exported from `runtime/__init__.py`\n- [ ] All tests pass with >80% coverage\n- [ ] Ruff lint passes\n- [ ] MyPy type check passes\n\n---\n\n## File Changes Summary\n\n| File | Action | Lines Changed | Description |\n|------|--------|---------------|-------------|\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | Create | ~120 | `BuildRuntime` class with build orchestration |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Modify | ~5 | Export `BuildRuntime` |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Modify | ~30 | Add `get_image_info`, `_format_size`, update `build_image` |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` | Modify | ~40 | Add `build` command with Typer options |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_runtime.py` | Create | ~200 | Unit tests for BuildRuntime |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_docker_service.py` | Modify | ~50 | Unit tests for new DockerService methods |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/test_build_integration.py` | Create | ~80 | Integration tests for build workflow |\n| `cmd/cli/pyproject.toml` | Modify | ~2 | Add `semver>=3.0.0` dependency |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n- **Design completed at Stage ST-3**\n- **Reference implementation**: `PackRuntime` in `pack_runtime.py` provides similar pattern\n- **DockerService already exists** with `check_docker_available` and `build_image` - enhance these\n- **semver library**: Use `semver.VersionInfo.parse()` and `bump_patch()` for version increment\n- **Version increment strategy**:\n  - Valid semver `X.Y.Z`: bump_patch → `X.Y.(Z+1)`\n  - v-prefixed semver `vX.Y.Z`: preserve prefix → `vX.Y.(Z+1)`\n  - v-prefixed non-semver `vX.Y`: append `.1` → `vX.Y.1`\n  - Non-semver string: append `-1` → `string-1`\n  - None/empty: use `\"latest\"`\n- **Proxy support**: Pass as `build_args={\"PROXY\": proxy_url}` to Docker SDK\n- **Rollback pattern**: Store original version, restore on exception\n- **Rich Progress**: Use `SpinnerColumn` + `TextColumn` for build spinner\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Timeline\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n|-------|-------|--------|------------|\n| Phase 1: DockerService Enhancements | T1.1, T1.2, T1.3, T1.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 2: BuildRuntime Class | T2.1, T2.2, T2.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 3: Version Increment Logic | T3.1, T3.2 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 4: Build Execution Methods | T4.1, T4.2, T4.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 5: CLI Command Implementation | T5.1, T5.2 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 6: Unit Tests - BuildRuntime | T6.1-T6.7 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 7: Unit Tests - DockerService | T7.1-T7.4 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 8: Integration Tests | T8.1-T8.3 | Pending | 0% |\n| Phase 9: Dependencies & Validation | T9.1-T9.4 | Pending | 0% |\n\n**Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/29 tasks)**"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_2026041